                        "type": "offensive_action",
                        "text": "The caligni stalker makes two Strikes against the same target, one with each of their shortswords. The stalker combines the damage of any attacks that hit and applies <a aonid=\"340\" game-obj=\"Rules\"><i>precision damage</i></a>, <a aonid=\"346\" game-obj=\"Rules\"><i>resistances</i></a>, and <a aonid=\"345\" game-obj=\"Rules\"><i>weaknesses</i></a> only once. Both attacks count toward the stalker\u2019s multiple attack penalty, but the penalty increases only after both attacks.",
